videos.headline: Grier to Brown for the Mountaineers touchdown
videos.description: Will Grier tosses a pass to Leddie Brown, who carries it in for a 15-yard West Virginia touchdown.

videos.headline: Brown gets second TD of the day
videos.description: West Virginia's Leddie Brown runs the ball in for a 1-yard touchdown, his second of the day.

videos.headline: Saunders gets first Kansas TD of day
videos.description: Mavin Saunders catches an 18-yard touchdown to decrease Kansas' deficit to 14-7 in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Haskins dives for West Virginia TD
videos.description: Jovani Haskins catches a pass from Will Grier and proceeds to dive in for the 14-yard Mountaineers touchdown.

videos.headline: Herbert runs for 31-yard Kansas touchdown
videos.description: Khalil Herbert takes the ball right up the middle practically untouched for a Jayhawks touchdown.

videos.headline: Grier finds Pettaway for West Virginia TD
videos.description: Will Grier finds Martell Pettaway wide open for the 12-yard touchdown, putting West Virginia up 28-14.

videos.headline: Kansas completes pass despite West Virginia dropping all 11 players
videos.description: Kanas completes a pass although all 11 Mountaineers dropped back from the snap and nobody passed the rush.
